Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.17,0:00:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When you watch Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep your room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.51,0:00:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you have a rival? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.47,0:00:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someone you don't want to lose to,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}whether it's in sports, school,\Nor some lessons you're taking.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With feelings like that,\Nwe improve very quickly, right?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:39.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As for myself, I aspired \Nto be like Miss Layla,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.26,0:00:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and so I've kept motivating\Nmyself to perform better until now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been trying not to lose to\Nmyself, and I've kept working hard,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I've never really thought that\NI don't want to lose to someone else.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, since May joined Kaleido Stage... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is not the time to say things like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's not! It's not!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the beginning\Nis red and black passions{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.29,0:01:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometimes, we rely on our contrary hearts{\i0}*
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.61,0:01:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss, the last resort is a\Nmission which changes the future{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.86,0:01:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There is no place for\Nambiguous answers in love{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.93,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even while pretending not to\Nsee the impossible reality, we bet{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hard-to-obtain-truth\NCan you feel me now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.24,0:01:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What should I say to myself,\Nwho gets excited easily?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.60,0:01:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm confused about what to say {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dreamin' the never-waking\Ndream, the falling fate{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.21,0:02:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't stop lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NYa ya ya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.51,0:02:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I believe in you, even\Nif I lose everything for it{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still lovin' can't stop lovin' you\NNo no no{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.20,0:02:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tattoo Kiss {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.96,0:02:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It just flashed across my mind\Nwhen I was looking at Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.07,0:02:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought this had to be our new production!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a horror story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Horror story?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means there won't be any gags.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.24,0:02:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:02:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"The Amazing Passionate Rival."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.30,0:03:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though it's a horror story,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's also a mysterious \Nand beautiful love story.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love story?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.44,0:03:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wandering around night after night\Nlooking for beautiful women's blood:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Count Dracula!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.51,0:03:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.60,0:03:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A beautiful woman who's attracted\Nto him, even while she's afraid of him:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.21,0:03:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Mina Murray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.75,0:03:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What? What? What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Guided by fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the two get together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:24.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's so romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.60,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Don't take this the wrong way, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is beyond my control...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This is good, Mia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've never done\Nanything like this before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hearing you say that\Ngives me a little confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, this was the first time\NI wrote a script imagining somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but there are no gags!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina Murray...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.10,0:03:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Miss Layla played her role,\Nit would have been wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.87,0:03:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}you're {\i0}the Kaleido Star now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But my time was decreased again yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote Mina Murray's\Ncharacter thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.82,0:03:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I even have a new spin maneuver,\Nsince those are your specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Leon sees your Mina Murray,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.67,0:04:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even he can't say he\Nwants to decrease your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.88,0:04:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, Leon decided to stay here\Nafter saying that he was leaving for France.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't think it's like\Nhe doesn't acknowledge you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be confident.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.62,0:04:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.77,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To answer Miss Layla's \Nexpectations, I should...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the first time,\NI aspired to be like somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.45,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to appear on stage with Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work hard for Rosetta too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she came to Kaleido Stage\Nbecause she wants to be like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's Rosetta doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's in her room, studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In her room?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since she has work, she said she's\Nalways been tutored by a computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard she's never been to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.29,0:04:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like she has to go through a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Leon?\NI think it's interesting, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Dracula?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.91,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.78,0:05:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time someone\Ncaptured me in this light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, um... In other words?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask you to revise it,\Nbut I don't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.82,0:05:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.30,0:05:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Mia!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.15,0:05:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I did it! Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Getting Mr. Leon's okay, \Nyou're something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.26,0:05:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Revise it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Where should I revise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.86,0:05:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.19,0:05:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get rid of her? You mean, completely?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.18,0:05:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.21,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mina Murray's climax, Screw Spin,\Nis a very difficult maneuver,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.62,0:05:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I think Sora can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think the audience will enjoy\Nwatching the maneuver as a main highlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satisfy me instead of the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.53,0:06:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't do it, I'll handle\Nthe leading role by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please see my Screw Spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can show you a\Nperformance that will satisfy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.05,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Double door open!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one person can satisfy Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.78,0:06:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next Layla Hamilton, {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning,\NI wrote this role thinking of Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.64,0:06:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's natural that the person who has\Nthe best abilities should get the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.07,0:06:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, naturally, this role is {\i1}mine{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you until tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care which one. Satisfy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying you have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, please leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll prepare the swing for practice tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, the time to compete has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though he said we have one day,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there's only one practice swing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.63,0:07:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In short, I can actually\Npractice only a half day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With her abilities, May may be\Nable to master the Screw Spin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.07,0:07:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I cannot allow myself to lose this game!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.21,0:07:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will win the game by all means.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now that Miss Layla's gone, the\None who'll be the Kaleido Star is me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.74,0:07:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can be no one else! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anna?! What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.74,0:07:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.72,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Powerful Pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.15,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Feng Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.17,0:07:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I move into this room\Nfor today and tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a better chance \Nof winning the duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I will move into this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.02,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's only for today and tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.07,0:08:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have to bring in my stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire Cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to win the duel,\NI need the heat of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing stir-fry is the best for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.40,0:08:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So there you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.47,0:08:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a Chinese dish for this morning's menu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.52,0:08:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Chinese dish in the early morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.04,0:08:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Greasy Chinese?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.55,0:08:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it good once in a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May was kind enough to cook for us. So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.36,0:08:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, so she only cooked for herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.49,0:08:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.64,0:08:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will cook for everybody now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please wait for a little while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's the swing for the Screw Spin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.24,0:08:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grand Screw Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:58.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:09:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In just one hour, she\Nmanaged to get to that point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's supposed to be a \Npretty difficult maneuver.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.84,0:09:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she's not all talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora could also get that far\Neasily if she practiced for an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.53,0:09:10.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know if I can do \Nit, but I have to try.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to take turns every\Nhour, so it's your turn next hour, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.52,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May, your hour's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Switch with Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do... Do you understand what I said?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I came here one\Nhour early and started practicing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because breakfast was late...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.84,0:09:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you shamelessly show\Nup now, trying to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so naïve!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you will not let Sora practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the only way you can win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not some swing in a park.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to take turns?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember agreeing\Nto anything like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, usually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't they usually say,\N"First come, first served"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is controlled \Nby the law of the jungle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon doesn't acknowledge you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.40,0:10:07.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm the only one \Nwho should take the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.19,0:10:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful to think he asked\Nyou to take the test out of pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.42,0:10:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.66,0:10:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.25,0:10:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, why don't you say something to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.24,0:10:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not acknowledged by Mr. Leon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still, I want to do what\NI can to make Kaleido Stage better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.09,0:10:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to take\Ntomorrow's test by all means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I intend to attempt it with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I consider you a friend who's\Ngoing to create Kaleido Stage with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.68,0:10:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.86,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.06,0:10:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just looking at your face makes me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.07,0:10:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single thing you do is disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.06,0:10:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.60,0:10:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be the one who performed the\Nlegendary great maneuver with Miss Layla?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were there, without a doubt,\NMiss Layla would have chosen me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.30,0:11:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not be outdone by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.08,0:11:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By taking this upcoming test, I'll prove\Nto everyone that I'm better than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How can you be the one who performed the\Nlegendary great maneuver with Miss Layla?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.41,0:11:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I were there, without a doubt,\NMiss Layla would have chosen me too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.29,0:11:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yet... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.43,0:11:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time, Miss Layla and \NI were real partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.92,0:11:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was positive there was nobody\Nelse who could be Miss Layla's partner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.41,0:11:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and perform the legendary\Ngreat maneuver except me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:11:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:02.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be my dream, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.04,0:12:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you can become a true Kaleido Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.49,0:12:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'm able to be\Na true Kaleido Star, Fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's up to you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.33,0:12:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is a true Kaleido Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I don't know the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.11,0:12:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you must find for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the only thing\Ncertain is that you can see me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.17,0:12:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora? Please come for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.58,0:12:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.71,0:12:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This... this is the swing for the Screw Spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.96,0:12:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, since I put this together so quickly,\Nit doesn't have enough height, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:04.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo-ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get beaten by somebody like May.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone helped build \Nthis just for you, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. After all,\NI still want you to play Mina Murray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.69,0:13:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mortifying if you lose without\Neven having a chance to practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.98,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia... Anna...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora is a Kaleido Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you motivated now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.23,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.09,0:13:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's Sora for you!\N--Always quick to recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.72,0:13:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all thanks to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.74,0:13:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, I don't have \Ntime to doubt myself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:13:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just have to do it! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's with this swing?! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even someone like Sora is having\Na hard time grasping the timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, she needs to get\Nused to this special swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, I see. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.84,0:14:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This swing turns around easily. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.45,0:14:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But once it starts turning, it can't stop.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.93,0:14:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It spins too fast. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.46,0:14:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know the timing\Nof when I should jump out.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:31.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But May was able to master\Nit this far in only one hour.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.33,0:14:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So... If I don't work hard now,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't be able to face everyone\Nwho's expecting me to do well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.22,0:14:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll end up disappointing Miss Layla\Nwho acknowledged me as a partner!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost there, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.56,0:15:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora's Sagittarius.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May's Taurus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leon's Scorpio.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.13,0:15:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a beautiful balance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if this balance is lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.33,0:15:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone will fall to the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--One more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Until I can do it perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Until I can do it perfectly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.17,0:16:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I have a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's because of the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.16,0:16:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just have to do it. I have to! I have to!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.78,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, we're going to start testing now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.79,0:17:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.60,0:17:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My body feels heavy. I've got chills.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anyhow, I have to give this\Nmy best shot. I have to! I have to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no... I'm getting dizzy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.56,0:18:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, that's all you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were not supposed\Nto be Miss Layla's partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.78,0:18:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'll show you how a\Nreal Kaleido Star performs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.39,0:18:37.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.46,0:18:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Mr. Leon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How was my performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.44,0:18:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I passed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even worth discussing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! I didn't make a mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.84,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I practiced so hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.90,0:19:13.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My performance was better than Sora's!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.24,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Leon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.28,0:19:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He never practiced the Screw Spin...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.61,0:19:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he can do a proper\Nperformance without practice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.23,0:20:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so full of yourself\Njust because you beat her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be my partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.25,0:20:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then shine as brilliantly\Nas I do. Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.96,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.60,0:20:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our level is too different. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.91,0:20:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, you have a fever, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes. But, it's not that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.33,0:20:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true. Your face is red, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.63,0:20:35.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you failed, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.74,0:20:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.35,0:20:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rewrite the script for Dracula.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.77,0:20:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the only star in the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.76,0:20:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Leon, Sora has a fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--She practiced in the rain yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please give her one more chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.43,0:20:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's not because of my temperature.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.81,0:20:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Everyone, really, you don't need to...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all lukewarm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So lukewarm, you make me sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew Kaleido Stage was a\Nplace with such a lukewarm attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.25,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I finally understand why Layla\NHamilton chose you for her partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ultimately, it means Layla Hamilton\Nwas also a lukewarm performer like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.31,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a half-baked top star who\Ncouldn't lose her rich girl attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.39,0:21:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't be tough on others or herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.38,0:21:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, that she chose \Nsomeone like you as a partner
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.81,0:21:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,means she was beyond recovery.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.08,0:21:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think an easy place like Kaleido\NStage was a perfect place for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.77,0:21:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know nothing about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.98,0:21:43.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you say that about Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.97,0:21:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.78,0:21:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You can say whatever you want about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.27,0:21:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.22,0:21:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--but Miss Layla isn't like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.56,0:21:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.21,0:21:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize! Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.97,0:21:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.43,0:21:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm mortified.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.63,0:22:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla was labeled\Nlike that because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.00,0:22:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have no choice but to work harder.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So everyone thinks I'm a\Nworthy partner for Miss Layla.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.28,0:22:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I found something I have to do. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For that, I'll make that man... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.79,0:22:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll make Leon... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}acknowledge me... {\i0}
